        <title>Stop, Tail, Turn and Hazard Lights</title>
        <para>This set of circuits contains the turn signal switch, stop light switch, flasher unit (turn
            signal/hazard), right and left turn relays, stop light relay, and right and left stop, turn, and tail light
            assemblies for the rear of the vehicle. The turn indicators located in the instrument cluster are also
            included.
        </para>
